\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"Paid press releases\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"Advertise\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 142}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest sports news\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 220}, {\"ngram\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"the legal problems\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"other members\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 team\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP PublishedFeb 06, 2024, 11:46 PM UpdatedFeb 06, 2024, 11:46 PM PARIS - French investigators have opened a legal probe into the pay of Paris Olympics chief organiser Tony Estanguet, a legal source said Feb 6, in an embarrassing development six months before the Games begin.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975266853577246, \"rank\": 0.002124539360518868, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP PublishedFeb\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"11:46 PM UpdatedFeb\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"11:46 PM\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"a legal probe\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"the pay\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"an embarrassing development\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The enquiry by magistrates specialised in financial crimes began \\\"last week\\\" and will look into the manner in which Estanguet receives his pay as head of the organising committee, the source said on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The enquiry\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"magistrates\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"financial crimes\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"the manner\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"his pay\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the source\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"condition\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The triple gold medal-winning Olympic canoeist had so far been spared the legal problems that have embroiled other members of the Paris 2024 team.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The triple gold medal-winning Olympic canoeist\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the legal problems\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"other members\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His annual remuneration of 270,000 euros (S$390,098) before tax and bonuses was made public in 2018 after a furore over reports that he would receive almost double that amount.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His annual remuneration\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"270,000 euros\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"S$390,098\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"tax\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"bonuses\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"a furore\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"almost double that amount\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But according to revelations in the investigative newspaper Le Canard Enchaine last October, Estanguet uses his own company to bill the organising committee monthly, instead of drawing a salary.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"revelations\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigative newspaper\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Canard Enchaine\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"his own company\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"a salary\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for the committee said it was \\\"astonished\\\" by the investigation and denied that Estanguet was paid as an external consultant in order to avoid salary caps placed on charities.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A spokesperson\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"an external consultant\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"salary caps\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"charities\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The package and arrangements had been approved by the board and the economy ministry, the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The package\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"arrangements\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"the economy ministry\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"the spokesperson\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The probe is a major blow for the suave 45-year-old Estanguet, the public face of the Paris Olympics, who is seeking to focus attention on preparations for the sporting events at the July 26-August 11 Games.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The probe\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"a major blow\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"the suave 45-year-old Estanguet\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the public face\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting events\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 26-August 11 Games\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics have been repeatedly tarnished by corruption in the past, either over the manner in which the Games were awarded or through the lucrative construction and services contracts that are part of the event.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"the manner\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the lucrative construction and services contracts\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The financial crimes prosecutors' office in Paris declined to comment when contacted by AFP.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6189352708976564e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9869724701238389, \"rank\": 0.013199486571351487, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The financial crimes prosecutors' office\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris organising committee was already the subject of three separate investigations into the possible misuse of public money and favouritism in the awarding of contracts.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6189352708976564e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"three separate investigations\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the possible misuse\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"favouritism\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"the awarding\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"contracts\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The offices of the committee and Games infrastructure group Solideo have been searched by police, as have the homes of two other senior figures in the organising committee, Etienne Thobois and Edouard Donnelly.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"score\": 0.9999993218032185, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Etienne Thobois\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The offices\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee and Games infrastructure group Solideo\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the homes\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"two other senior figures\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"Edouard Donnelly\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those cases revolve in part around sports management or events companies founded by senior Games staff before they started working for the Paris 2024 organising committee.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those cases\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"sports management or events companies\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"senior Games staff\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 20 different contracts are under the microscope, totalling tens of million of euros, one judicial source told AFP on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9869724701238389, \"rank\": 0.013199486571351487, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 20 different contracts\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"the microscope\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"euros\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"one judicial source\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"condition\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's Anti-Corruption Agency had flagged possible problems with Estanguet's pay arrangement in a report in 2021 because of the organising committee's status as a charity.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997231984748955, \"rank\": 0.0002747446045722104, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbp