\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"his remuneration\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"the spokesperson\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers of Paris 2024 have been determined to showcase a different sort of Olympics, shorn of the common problems of vast over-spending, wasteful infrastructure investment, and corruption.\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"a different sort\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"the common problems\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"vast over-spending\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"wasteful infrastructure investment\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a speech last month, President Emmanuel Macron called them \\\"a unique opportunity to show the best of ourselves, obviously in the sporting world... but also what our country represents and knows what to do in terms of exemplarity and organisation.\\\"\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3661, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a speech\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique opportunity\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3710}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting world\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3802}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"exemplarity\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"organisation\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the French Anti-Corruption Agency and the state's top auditor body were given oversight of the organising committee in a bid to root out graft.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 4027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975266853577246, \"rank\": 0.002124539360518868, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the state's top auditor body\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"oversight\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3971}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 3999}, {\"ngram\": \"a bid\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4008}, {\"ngram\": \"graft\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2016 Rio Olympics featured large-scale corruption, which shocked the general public, leading the former Brazilian Olympics boss and the governor of the city to be convicted afterwards.\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7560332809075118e-19, \"text\": \"2016 Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"large-scale corruption\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"the general public\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4116}, {\"ngram\": \"the former Brazilian Olympics boss\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"the governor\", \"from\": 4165, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several businessmen were also found guilty of bribing a Tokyo Olympics committee member in a scandal that soured the mood over the 2020 Games held in the Japanese capital.\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998640305, \"rank\": 1.360336612173999e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4373, \"end\": 4381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999849265445034, \"rank\": 8.567720969712338e-06, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several businessmen\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"a scandal\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"the mood\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Games\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the legal problems, the Paris Games appear broadly on track, with almost all of the main building work finished and the budget over-spend relatively small compared with past editions.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legal problems\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4418}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"almost all\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4476}, {\"ngram\": \"the main building work\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"t